_sText:
Hi there. It's been a minute so I hope this works. Here's just a simple redo of the classic fy_funtimes originally done by the impeccable Stryker. Earliest known upload on gamebanana is Sept 25, 2005 by exaN. A couple of notes:

HDR lighting and textures.
Some texture and asset imports from CSGO.
Some custom (original) textures.
Bumped max players up to 40 (being mindful of spawn kill placement).
Added a few cubemaps.
Added generic ambience.
Added a radar material.

Packed with VIDE. Please let me know if you can't see something!
I encourage critique and questions.

Credits/links:
gamebanana.com/members/48469
Nothing fancy; just a good, fun time.
